The Smoldering Corpse is a bar+in+Sigil's Hive Ward, once known for the man-shaped figure consumed by fire over a huge grill in the center of the building. The figure heated the bar as well as all the grills in the kitchen.
The flaming figure, Ignus, was later freed by the Nameless One.
